{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_16","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":16,"text":"And these were the sons of Juda, according to their families: to Selom the family of the Selonites; to Phares, the family of the Pharesites; to Zara, the family of the Zaraites.","searchKeywords":["and","these","were","the","sons","juda","according","their","families","selom","family","selonites","phares","pharesites","zara","zaraites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_17","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":17,"text":"And the sons of Phares were, to Asron, the family of the Asronites; to Jamun, the family of the Jamunites.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","phares","were","asron","family","asronites","jamun","jamunites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_18","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":18,"text":"These the families of Juda according to their numbering, seventy-six thousand and five hundred.","searchKeywords":["these","the","families","juda","according","their","numbering","seventy","six","thousand","and","five","hundred"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_19","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":19,"text":"And the sons of Issachar according to their families: to Thola, the family of the Tholaites; to Phua, the family of the Phuaites.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","issachar","according","their","families","thola","family","tholaites","phua","phuaites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_20","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":20,"text":"To Jasub, the family of the Jasubites; to Samram, the family of the Samramites.","searchKeywords":["jasub","the","fami