e Addites:","searchKeywords":["azeni","the","family","azenites","addi","addites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_26","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":26,"text":"to Aroadi, the family of the Aroadites; to Ariel, the family of the Arielites.","searchKeywords":["aroadi","the","family","aroadites","ariel","arielites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_27","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":27,"text":"These the families of the children of Gad according to their numbering, forty-four thousand and five hundred.","searchKeywords":["these","the","families","children","gad","according","their","numbering","forty","four","thousand","and","five","hundred"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_28","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":28,"text":"The sons of Aser according to their families; to Jamin, the family of the Jaminites; to Jesu, the family of the Jesusites; to Baria, the family of the Bariaites.","searchKeywords":["the","sons","aser","according","their","families","jamin","family","jaminites","jesu","jesusites","baria","bariaites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_29","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":29,"text":"To Chober, the family of the Choberites; to Melchiel, the family of the Melchielites.","searchKeywords":["chober","the","family","choberites","melchiel","melchielites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_30","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":30,"text":"And the name of the daughter of Aser, Sara.","searchKeywords":["and","the","name","daughter","aser","sara"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_31","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookInd