Opher, the family of the Opherites.","searchKeywords":["symaer","the","family","symaerites","and","opher","opherites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_37","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":37,"text":"And to Salpaad the son of Opher there were no sons, but daughters: and these the names of the daughters of Salpaad; Mala, and Nua, and Egla, and Melcha, and Thersa.","searchKeywords":["and","salpaad","the","son","opher","there","were","sons","but","daughters","these","names","mala","nua","egla","melcha","thersa"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_38","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":38,"text":"These the families of Manasse according to their numbering, fifty-two thousand and seven hundred.","searchKeywords":["these","the","families","manasse","according","their","numbering","fifty","two","thousand","and","seven","hundred"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_39","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":39,"text":"And these the children of Ephraim; to Suthala, the family of the Suthalanites; to Tanach, the family of the Tanachites.","searchKeywords":["and","these","the","children","ephraim","suthala","family","suthalanites","tanach","tanachites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_40","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":40,"text":"These the sons of Suthala; to Eden, the family of the Edenites.","searchKeywords":["these","the","sons","suthala","eden","family","edenites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_41","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":41,"text":"These the families of Ephraim according to their numbering, thirty-two thousand and five hundred: these the 