r families; to Same, the family of the Sameites; these the families of Dan according to their families.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","dan","according","their","families","same","family","sameites","these"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_47","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":47,"text":"All the families of Samei according to their numbering, sixty-four thousand and four hundred.","searchKeywords":["all","the","families","samei","according","their","numbering","sixty","four","thousand","and","hundred"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_48","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":48,"text":"The sons of Nephthali according to their families; to Asiel, the family of the Asielites; to Gauni, the family of the Gaunites.","searchKeywords":["the","sons","nephthali","according","their","families","asiel","family","asielites","gauni","gaunites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_49","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":49,"text":"To Jeser, the family of the Jeserites; to Sellem, the family of the Sellemites.","searchKeywords":["jeser","the","family","jeserites","sellem","sellemites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_50","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":50,"text":"These the families of Nephthali, according to their numbering, forty thousand and three hundred.","searchKeywords":["these","the","families","nephthali","according","their","numbering","forty","thousand","and","three","hundred"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_51","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":51,"text":"This the numbering of the children of Israel, six hundred and one thousand and seven hundred and thirty.","searchKeywords":["this","the","numbering","children","israel","six","hundred","and","one","thousand","seven","thirty"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_52","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":52,"text":"And the Lord spoke to Moses, saying,","searchKeywords":["and","the","lord","spoke","moses","saying"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_53","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":53,"text":"To these the land shall be divided, so that they may inherit according to the number of the names.","searchKeywords":["these","the","land","shall","divided","that","they","may","inherit","according","number","names"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_54","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":54,"text":"To the greater number thou shalt give the greater inheritance, and to the less number thou shalt give the less inheritance: to each one, as they have been numbered, shall their inheritance be given.","searchKeywords":["the","greater","number","thou","shalt","give","inheritance","and","less","each","one","they","have","been","numbered","shall","their","given"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_55","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":55,"text":"The land shall be divided to the names by lot, they shall inherit according to the tribes of their families.","searchKeywords":["the","land","shall","divided","names","lot","they","inherit","according","tribes","their","families"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_56","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":56,"text":"Thou shalt divide their inheritance by lot between the many and the few.","searchKeywords":["thou","shalt","divide","their","inheritance","lot","between","the","many","and","few"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_57","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":57,"text":"And the sons of Levi according to their families; to Gedson, the family of the Gedsonites; to Caath, the family of the Caathites; to Merari, the family of the Merarites.","searchKeywords":["and","the","sons","levi","according","their","families","gedson","family","gedsonites","caath","caathites","merari","merarites"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_58","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":58,"text":"These the families of the sons of Levi; the family of the Lobenites, the family of the Chebronites, the family of the Coreites, and the family of the Musites; and Caath begot Amram.","searchKeywords":["these","the","families","sons","levi","family","lobenites","chebronites","coreites","and","musites","caath","begot","amram"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_59","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":59,"text":"And the name of his wife Jochabed, daughter of Levi, who bore these to Levi in Egypt, and she bore to Amram, Aaron and Moses, and Mariam their sister.","searchKeywords":["and","the","name","his","wife","jochabed","daughter","levi","who","bore","these","egypt","she","amram","aaron","moses","mariam","their","sister"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_60","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":60,"text":"And to Aaron were born both Nadab and Abiud, and Eleazar, and Ithamar.","searchKeywords":["and","aaron","were","born","both","nadab","abiud","eleazar","ithamar"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_61","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":61,"text":"And Nadab and Abiud died when they offered strange fire before the Lord in the wilderness of Sina.","searchKeywords":["and","nadab","abiud","died","when","they","offered","strange","fire","before","the","lord","wilderness","sina"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_62","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":62,"text":"And there were according to their numbering, twenty-three thousand, every male from a month old and upward; for they were not numbered among the children of Israel, because they have no inheritance in the midst of the children of Israel.","searchKeywords":["and","there","were","according","their","numbering","twenty","three","thousand","every","male","from","month","old","upward","for","they","not","numbered","among","the","children","israel","because","have","inheritance","midst"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_63","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":63,"text":"And this the numbering of Moses and Eleazar the priest, who numbered the children of Israel in Araboth of Moab, at Jordan by Jericho.","searchKeywords":["and","this","the","numbering","moses","eleazar","priest","who","numbered","children","israel","araboth","moab","jordan","jericho"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_64","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":64,"text":"And among these there was not a man numbered by Moses and Aaron, whom, the children of Israel, they numbered in the wilderness of Sinai.","searchKeywords":["and","among","these","there","was","not","man","numbered","moses","aaron","whom","the","children","israel","they","wilderness","sinai"]},{"verseId":"brenton_numbers_26_65","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":4,"bookName":"Numbers","bookAbbrev":"numbers","chapter":26,"verse":65,"text":"For the Lord said to them, They shall surely die in the wilderness; and there was not left even one of them, except Chaleb the son of Jephonne, and Joshua the of Naue.","searchKeywords":["for","the","lord","said","them","they","shall","surely","die","wilderness","and","there","was","not","left","even","one","except","chaleb","son","jephonne","joshua","naue"]}]